| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5038 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 15115b29-fbb0-5a5d-9b9a-12317bd7b7f0"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
